  "texts": [
    "Similarly, threat intelligence is an advanced feature that is usually not considered by SMEs as they lack the financial and human resources to manage it.",
    "While active online community support is certainly beneficial, the documentation of the SIEM solutions is usually sufficient for configuration and troubleshooting.",
    "However, any SIEM solution that provides these secondary features will of course have an added advantage over others.",
    "Most SIEM solutions provide the log parsers for commonly used devices by default.",
    "However, at times we might need to integrate a custom data source whose parser is not available in the SIEM system."
  ],
